Semi-Permanent Brows

Perfect, natural-looking eyebrows that last

Semi-Permanent Brows Image Placeholder

Transform Your Look

Our semi-permanent brow treatments use the latest techniques to create beautifully shaped, natural-looking eyebrows that enhance your facial features. Perfect for those with sparse, over-plucked, or uneven brows.

Services Include:

  • Microblading
  • Powder Brows
  • Combination Brows
  • Brow Mapping & Design
  • Touch-up Sessions

Benefits:

  • Save time on daily makeup routine
  • Natural, hair-like strokes
  • Lasts 12-18 months
  • Custom color matching
  • Professional consultation included

Treatment Information

Duration: 2-3 hours

Healing Time: 7-14 days

Touch-up Required: 4-6 weeks after initial treatment

Pricing: Contact us for detailed pricing
